messages.message:
<!here> Hey team! Want to help out with the Goldman Production Release for March 27th? Help us build our golden datasets!

For starters, it would be great if you could help us annotate 10 documents for a particular document type:

What I’m asking:
   1. Put your name next to “Status” for one of the document types
   2. Read the instructions
   3. Complete 10 documents and let us know when you are done!

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FYbPsxeyvCg_oItc41XFQzkYaEp8iHoesBEDlVJJEeQ/edit#

It takes a little bit of time to understand the document format; but once you do; it might take 1 - 2 hours to annotate these 10 documents

Please let me know if you can help (we need it); we are looking to compare against these golden answers over the weekend, then Monday, and we will iterate on them until Wednesday
